        "text": "In general, research and development activities are conducted by specialized units or centers belonging to a company, or can be [[out-sourced]] to a contract research organization, [[universities]], or state ([[sovereign state]]) agencies. In the context of [[commerce]], \"research and development\" normally refers to future-oriented, longer-term activities in [[science]] or [[technology]], using similar techniques to scientific research but directed toward desired outcomes and with broad forecasts of commercial yield."
